{"type": "article", "id": 15325, "title": "固定物品的包", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-23T06:50:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061435069FL6C2Mcd8lVrf1Y.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款包其实也很经典，能将所有物品固定起来。它的表面横竖布满了弹性橡胶带，可以将任何型号的物品固定住。不仅能让它们一目了然，也避免了相互干扰。对于相机、硬盘等电子产品来说，也减少了因旅途颠簸带来的损耗。这款包不同大小的型号，都有黑、灰两种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://www.cocooninnovations.com/cat_info.php?cat_id=61\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142536S2stxCQdoXBVjPZl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"456\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142536VQMCKuclD4oSihIX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"823\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142537JhiFewfcvVaqX7Ol.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"274\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}